choices.text:
Create a csv of the first 5 presidents of the United states with their names, age when they started office, year they started office, and number of years they served
Sure! Here is an example CSV file that includes data for all 50 US Presidents in chronological order. Each row represents one President's information, including his name, birthdate (if available), the date he was inaugurated as president, and how many terms he has been serving since then.
